Package functions.unitary

Class UnitaryFunction

Object
GeneralFunction
UnitaryFunction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Differentiable, Evaluable, Simplifiable, Comparable<GeneralFunction>, Iterable<GeneralFunction>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Factorial, GeneralTrigFunction, PiecewiseFunction, SpecialCaseBinaryFunction, Transformation
public abstract class UnitaryFunction
extends GeneralFunction
The abstract UnitaryFunction class represents function of one input. Ex: cos or abs
